{
  "texts": [
    "FinLMEval (Guo et al., 2023) and DISC-FinLLM (Chen et al., 2023) focus on evaluation and model performance in monetary scenarios.",
    "Other work, such as Chu et al. (2023), emphasizes sophisticated data preprocessing for better handling of financial tasks.",
    "Appendix A provides a further discussion of the NLP and LLMs literature in finance.",
    "We develop comprehensive and diverse datasets to build FinTral.",
    "We first describe our raw datasets rich in domain-specific tokens, setting a solid foundation for model training, then our instruction finetuning and AI-driven feedback datasets."
  ]
}